    "Name": "Vindicator",
    "Details": "A rebuild of the -1R with more powerful technology, the Vindicator VND-2R replaces the PPC with an Extended Range version and upgrades the LRM launcher to 15 Artemis IV-enabled tubes. To free the needed weight capacity for the upgrades the chassis uses a Endo Steel structure, the armor to Ferro-Fibrous and the small laser was dropped.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Rugged</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
